          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Beyond the Box for Higher Education Act of </b> <b>2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education to issue guidance and recommendations for institutions of higher education to remove criminal and juvenile justice questions from their admission applications.</p>]]>
